videos.headline: Gators recover fumble on mishandled snap
videos.description: Florida capitalizes on a fumbled snap by the Colorado State punter, later leading to a field goal for the Gators.

videos.headline: Florida QB picked off on great defensive read
videos.description: Gators quarterback Feleipe Franks unloads a deep ball over the middle of the field and is intercepted by Rams DB V.J. Banks.

videos.headline: Gators RB finds a seam for 30-yard TD
videos.description: Florida running back Jordan Scarlett slithers his way between Rams defenders and sprints to the house for a 30-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Gators QB fires a TD strike
videos.description: Florida quarterback Feleipe Franks grooves a missile to his receiver Freddie Swain for an 18-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Gators topple on blocked punt for TD
videos.description: Florida blocks Colorado State's punt attempt and sends a pack of Gators to the end zone, recovering the ball for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Colorado State finally scores first TD vs. Florida
videos.description: Rams quarterback K.J. Carta-Samuels zips a pass to his tight end Trey McBride, who sheds a tackle and fights into the end zone for a 48-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Franks on the money with 38-yard dime
videos.description: Gators quarterback Feleipe Franks flings a 38-yard pass to wide receiver Van Jefferson for a touchdown to open the flood gates vs. Colorado State, 41-10.

videos.headline: Gators RB cracks off 68-yard TD run
videos.description: Florida running back Dameon Pierce piles it on with a 68-yard touchdown dash, the Gators' longest play of the season.
